-- Czech PPF buys further 7.2 pct shares in O2 Czech Republic
-- By Robert Muller
-- Mon Jul 07, 2014 02:48AM EDT
-- None



PRAGUE, July 7 (Reuters) - Czech financial group PPF has bought an additional 7.16 percent of the shares in mobile operator O2 Czech Republic <SPTT.PR>, formerly Telefonica Czech Republic, the group said on Monday, without saying what it had paid for the stake.

